AI is extremely expensive. The current wave of global marketing and free access is temporary. The cost curves will force consolidation.

AI will follow the blockchain pattern.

Enterprise: competitive advantage for companies with capital.

SMB: embedded inside off‑the‑shelf products, not built internally.

